summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2010 ALUM-LINE FLATBED TRAILER (NA). THE CONTACT STATED THAT WHEN THE TRAILER WAS LOADED, THERE WAS AN ABNORMAL CRACK AT THE GOOSE NECK SECTION OF THE TRAILER HITCH. THE TRAILER WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS APPROXIMATELY 500.
